abstract: "Three Claude Code skills for using Codex CLI in research and build workflows: codex-bridge for one-shot Codex calls, mad-build for staged Claude-Codex collaboration, and mad-research for adversarial audits of papers, grants, and reports with anonymized cross-critique and fresh-context synthesis."
